Ksp has been crashing on me all day can't figure out the cause. I tried running the game multiple times and it crashed loading so I made a backup of my saves and mods in use then uninstalled the game and deleted the leftover files in the steam library and reinstalled a fresh unmodded install. Game still hang's then crashes on loadup, verifying the integrity of the game comes up with missing files only after it crashes. I am out of ideas. I am using the current version of windows 10 and an evga gtx 660 factory overclocked with the most recent nvidia drivers they released may 9th, I also have 8gb of ram.

output log
